          "Strong leaders <strong>leverage different personality types</strong> — placing the natural communicator in front and giving direction-followers clear tasks maximizes the team (EI:104). Match roles to strengths.",
          "<strong>Consensus building</strong> is a structured process where the group reaches a decision everyone can support; the formal method starts by <strong>defining/discussing the issue</strong> before voting (EI:011)."
